overview: The user initiated a request for thorough browser-based testing of the
  sleep questionnaire application. The agent began by verifying the dev server
  status and navigating the application. Key testing areas included the main
  questionnaire flow, report generation, and the admin dashboard. During the
  questionnaire testing, the agent utilized a "Pre-fill & Jump to Report (Dev)"
  feature to expedite testing of the report section, successfully verifying PDF
  download functionality. For the admin section, after being redirected to a
  login page and unable to access environment variables for credentials, the
  agent proceeded to test the login error handling with an incorrect password,
  which worked as expected. A notable issue discovered was the inability to
  navigate past the initial "Intro" section of the questionnaire using the "Next
  Section" button, even though no console errors were present.
